{"type": "article", "id": 3746, "title": "Dot and Cross 儿童家具", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-21T08:09:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233243V5gSnjQY1eZa0hOt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利设计事务所 Dogtrot 联手设计师 Daniele Bortotto 与 Giorgia Zanellato 创立了一个名为「Dot and Cross」的儿童家具品牌。浅色系的配色加以灵活的模块化组合形式，是 Dot and Cross 最新系列儿童家具的最大特点。很多购买儿童家具的消费者都会有这样的顾虑，随着孩子慢慢成长，买回家的儿童家具便不再适用了，而 Dot and Cross 则希望通过这个系列传递出成长的意义，如一款幼年时适用的画板可以随着孩子入学变身成为书桌，而婴儿床在拆掉栅栏后可以承担沙发的功能，书架与置物架的模块化设置也给用户提供了更多的组合方案，衣柜也拥有可变的高度与宽度。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233240rsVjyBNtLvmSY5Jw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233240vdCOmRcGwH5elFao.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233241Zu6bK05YCOPlR1qr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233241zh4R0LwG69l8gMEB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233242H3rdQMiatU7euGAX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233242y9BUCdS8j5GPrsaY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}